Freshly painted throughout the home, with open large 14' ceilings in the Living Room and formal Dining room.  Granite Countertops. Storm Shelter.  ENORMOUS Bonus room upstairs for the man cave.  Nice storage shop built into the back of the house as well.  Really great find on just enough land.  Call or Text today to schedule your personal tour!
